      "content": "hey i need help... im seeing stuff on my twitter and insta that i definitely didnt post. like the tone is exactly like me but the thoughts are weird and i didnt write them. is it actually possible for some ai to just... hijack someone's identity and pretend to be them this perfectly? it feels like im watching a ghost of myself online",
